If you go back and hear the 'Authority of the Believer' sermon series he had—he had a visitation from the Lord and was talking—all of a sudden this devil came out and started making noise.

00:25:06.799 --> 00:25:18.187
He was so frustrated because Jesus wouldn't do anything about the devil and he couldn't hear what the Lord was saying because the devil was making such a loud noise by his feet.

00:25:18.187 --> 00:25:23.240
He was like, 'Oh, I wish the Lord would do something about this devil.

00:25:23.240 --> 00:25:33.180
' Jesus was talking the whole time and he couldn't hear anything He was saying because He wouldn't take care of that devil for him.

00:25:33.180 --> 00:25:38.159
So, Brother Hagin said in the vision, 'In the name of Jesus, devil, get out of here!

00:25:38.159 --> 00:25:40.159
Shut up and go!

00:25:40.159 --> 00:25:45.333
' That devil took off and got out of there.

00:25:45.333 --> 00:25:48.018
He said, 'Why didn't You do anything about it?

00:25:48.018 --> 00:25:51.828
' Jesus said, 'I couldn't do anything about it.

00:25:51.828 --> 00:25:56.349
' He said, 'What do you mean You couldn't?

00:25:56.349 --> 00:26:03.240
' He said, 'I don't think I heard You correctly,' and they kept arguing back and forth.

00:26:03.240 --> 00:26:15.200
Basically, the bottom line is if he wouldn't take his authority and tell that devil to get out of here—Jesus already did it, and it took us to do it.

00:26:21.120 --> 00:26:24.400
The bottom line is that Christ gave you authority over the devil, and Jesus is not going to do any more about the devil.

00:26:24.400 --> 00:26:48.377
You're going to have to stand up against him with the sword of the Spirit and tell him, as James 4:7 says, 'Submit yourself therefore unto God, resist the devil and he will flee.

00:26:48.377 --> 00:26:57.497
' If you don't do that, he's going to sit there and nip at your feet.

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:08.640
That's why I tell you all the time to take your authority.

00:27:10.329 --> 00:27:12.320
That's why I have Sister Billye's books and we keep them all around.

00:27:12.320 --> 00:27:17.394
I've got them everywhere so that you understand the power of the authority of the believer.

00:27:17.394 --> 00:27:22.676
It's important because the Lord's not going to do anything else about the devil.

00:27:22.676 --> 00:27:35.885
He gave you power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions and nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:27:35.885 --> 00:27:39.324
Is that literal?

00:27:39.324 --> 00:27:51.387
I believe it's literal and metaphorical.

00:27:52.960 --> 00:28:36.630
I believe that Jesus gave me power and authority over the principalities and all of it concerning me and my house.

00:28:53.760 --> 00:28:55.200
I don't go around binding everything else out here or going into neighborhoods binding the devil and the principality over Tulsa.

00:29:42.620 --> 00:29:43.120
No, concerning me and my house, you have no power in my house.

00:29:53.200 --> 00:29:58.032
I pray over my president and my neighborhood, but I don't go to your house and start binding the principality of Persia and being stupid.

00:30:01.279 --> 00:30:07.186
I take authority over my house, my children, my wife, my finances, and my church.

00:30:18.639 --> 00:30:19.040
I pray over my pastors and our leaders, that You give them fresh revelation knowledge to teach the body of Christ.

00:30:19.040 --> 00:30:24.080
We pray over our leaders and we flow in that gift.

00:30:39.467 --> 00:30:39.796
Lord said, 'Keep it shorter.

00:30:39.796 --> 00:30:40.782
Pray more.

00:30:40.782 --> 00:30:43.885
' Father, we thank You for the body.

00:30:43.885 --> 00:30:51.999
We thank You, Lord, for all that You've done for us.

00:30:51.999 --> 00:30:57.063
We thank You that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:31:07.109 --> 00:31:07.360
We're so grateful for tongues and the interpretation of tongues.

00:31:07.360 --> 00:31:14.982
We're so grateful for the gifts of the Spirit, that we walk in divine healing and health.

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:23.440
We walk in the authority of the believer and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:31:23.440 --> 00:31:35.831
A thousand shall fall at our side and ten thousand at our right hand, but it shall not come nigh us.

00:31:35.831 --> 00:31:43.840
I believe for Psalm 91 to become a revelation in my life.

00:31:56.913 --> 00:31:57.290
I thank You, Lord, that I have eyes to see what You see and ears to hear what the Spirit is saying.

00:32:03.130 --> 00:32:05.590
Father, I thank You that I am filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:32:06.311 --> 00:32:21.360
We yield to the anointing of wealth, the prophetic, healing, deliverance, peace, and joy, and all the fruit of the Spirit: love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, gentleness, and self-control.

00:32:21.360 --> 00:32:27.439
Holy Spirit, flood my life with Your goodness and Your mercy.

00:32:27.439 --> 00:32:39.893
Goodness and mercy will follow me all the days of my life and I will dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

00:32:39.893 --> 00:33:12.399
Father, we thank You for this body and all You've done for us.

00:33:12.399 --> 00:33:33.311
We walk in divine health and nothing shall by any means hurt us in Jesus' name.

00:33:46.340 --> 00:33:50.310
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:33:50.320 --> 00:34:25.019
We make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

00:34:51.200 --> 00:35:08.000
I thank You, Father, that if we confess our sins, You are faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:35:08.000 --> 00:35:25.040
We plead the blood of Jesus over anything You show us.

00:35:25.040 --> 00:35:48.971
We thank You, Lord, that we only see what You want us to see, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:36:04.500 --> 00:36:04.840
I plead the blood of Jesus Christ over my spiritual and natural eyes.

00:36:04.840 --> 00:36:08.600
We are led by the Spirit of God.

00:36:08.600 --> 00:36:15.104
We tell our flesh to shut up.

00:36:15.104 --> 00:36:31.004
Father, I thank You for the blood that never loses its power, covering my family and even our dogs.

00:36:31.004 --> 00:36:55.435
We're so grateful that You've redeemed us and made us whole.

00:36:55.435 --> 00:37:15.430
We take this blood right now in Jesus' mighty name.

00:37:15.440 --> 00:37:16.977
Amen.

00:37:16.977 --> 00:37:20.820
Jesus Christ loves you.

00:37:20.820 --> 00:37:29.839
I'm not about religion; I'm about Jesus and a relationship.

00:37:30.791 --> 00:37:46.230
I want a God I can talk to and be friends with.

00:37:46.240 --> 00:37:54.693
Sister Billye just texted me.

00:37:54.693 --> 00:38:08.693
Father, I thank You for this night.

00:38:08.693 --> 00:38:16.800
I exalt Thee, oh Lord.

00:38:42.560 --> 00:38:43.248
For Thou, Lord, art high above all the earth; Thou art exalted far above all gods.

00:38:43.248 --> 00:38:52.510
There are no other gods; they're all just made-up devils.

00:38:52.510 --> 00:38:55.484
They just changed the lyrics of that song.

00:38:55.484 --> 00:38:56.409
Isn't that interesting?

00:38:56.409 --> 00:39:02.800
I love the song, but I don't like that verse.

00:39:02.800 --> 00:39:05.307
Father, we just thank you, Lord.

00:39:08.613 --> 00:39:10.777
There is no God before you.

00:39:10.777 --> 00:39:13.550
You are the only God.

00:39:13.550 --> 00:39:23.086
Everything else is just a demonic spirit trying to pretend.

00:39:23.086 --> 00:39:42.000
You are the Great I Am That I Am, and I'm so thankful that you dwell on the inside of me.

00:39:42.000 --> 00:40:03.312
I'm so grateful for all that you've called us to do.

00:40:03.312 --> 00:40:44.960
Father, I'm so grateful that you chose us and you say, 'Hey, I can trust you.

00:40:44.960 --> 00:41:21.780
' And I, Father, I'm so grateful, for the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart who's perfect toward you.

00:41:21.780 --> 00:41:44.190
I thank you, Lord, that our hearts are somewhere you do not have to look anymore.

00:41:51.229 --> 00:41:56.593
You look at us and you say, 'I see that they are ready.

00:41:56.593 --> 00:42:06.819
' Father, I thank you, Lord, that we're yielded by the spirit of God.

00:42:06.819 --> 00:42:49.501
For those that are called sons of God, those are led by the spirit of God.

00:42:49.501 --> 00:43:08.053
For those that are led by the spirit of God are the sons of God.

00:43:15.760 --> 00:43:16.583
And I thank you that we are led by the spirit of God.

00:43:16.583 --> 00:43:22.023
We're led by your spirit.

00:43:40.640 --> 00:43:40.915
For those that are led by the spirit of God, they are the sons and daughters of God.

00:43:41.742 --> 00:43:43.880
And tonight, we lift up our president before you.

00:43:43.880 --> 00:43:48.880
We lift up this need of the nation as he is in the valley of decision again.

00:43:49.930 --> 00:43:53.590
And you said this would be the make or break of the presidency.

00:43:53.590 --> 00:44:02.605
Lord, I don't know what kind of decisions he's making, but you said it.

00:44:21.359 --> 00:44:21.599
So, Father, we lift him up before you and we thank you, Lord, that he takes no counsel from the wicked.

00:44:21.599 --> 00:44:25.080
Father, we would be on that straight and narrow path.

00:44:27.108 --> 00:44:41.349
I thank you, Lord, that we would hear you and we would follow you, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:44:47.497 --> 00:44:53.853
And that's concerning even our president.

00:44:53.853 --> 00:45:09.850
We lift up this time before you, Father, in prayer.

00:45:38.240 --> 00:45:38.540
And we believe, Father, that your hand is on them and upon the cabinet.

00:45:38.540 --> 00:45:42.697
I see Marco Rubio before me right now.

00:45:45.440 --> 00:45:47.119
There's an anointing coming on Marco Rubio right now.

00:45:47.119 --> 00:45:49.976
Something is shifting with Marco Rubio.

00:45:49.976 --> 00:45:55.749
There is a glory coming on Marco Rubio.

00:46:01.373 --> 00:46:04.818
I see like a light shining on him and I see a heart that has become pliable before the Lord.

00:46:04.818 --> 00:46:06.240
Oh, a meekness.

00:46:06.507 --> 00:46:07.040
A meekness.

00:46:07.040 --> 00:46:13.956
Oh Lord, praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:46:13.956 --> 00:46:22.530
Oh, I can hear him singing, 'For your name is great and greatly to be praised.

00:46:22.530 --> 00:46:27.520
' I sing praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:46:27.520 --> 00:46:36.320
Praises to your name, oh Lord, for your name is great and greatly to be praised.

00:47:04.880 --> 00:47:05.176
I sing praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:47:05.176 --> 00:47:07.543
Praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:47:07.543 --> 00:47:09.417
I'll describe what I hear.

00:47:19.911 --> 00:47:20.213
I hear echoes upon waters and their voices that are singing in heaven.

00:47:23.270 --> 00:47:25.659
And it sounds like there are octaves, but they're all blending into one.

00:47:25.659 --> 00:47:32.399
As I hear them singing this, it fills the atmosphere and I can smell the fragrance of it.

00:47:32.399 --> 00:47:39.262
They're all blending into one voice, but they're different octaves, but they're one sound.

00:47:39.262 --> 00:47:49.920
There's not like a choir you can hear, and I don't want to leave it.

00:47:52.740 --> 00:47:56.754
I hear them.

00:47:56.754 --> 00:47:57.577
Oh Jesus.

00:48:00.880 --> 00:48:01.440
It sounds like a sound of water, but it floats.

00:48:13.907 --> 00:48:14.480
It all blends into one.

00:48:14.480 --> 00:48:22.1000
One sound, one voice, but many different voices that blend into one, singing: 'I sing praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:48:22.1000 --> 00:48:33.293
Praises to your name, oh Lord, for your name is great and greatly to be praised.

00:48:33.293 --> 00:48:36.210
I sing praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:48:36.210 --> 00:48:38.389
Praises to your name, oh Lord.

00:48:38.389 --> 00:48:44.159
' And what's amazing about it is there's these beautiful pink swirls with beautiful, beautiful colors.

00:48:44.159 --> 00:48:57.040
They look like song notes, but they're rippling like you would see animation for the wind, and it's being carried on the wind.

00:48:57.040 --> 00:49:07.059
It comes in and comes out.

00:49:07.059 --> 00:49:12.930
You know how you feel the wind and it wisps, it whispers.

00:49:12.930 --> 00:49:20.610
You know, you can feel, you can hear it, but there's no end and there's no beginning to it.

00:49:20.610 --> 00:49:26.286
It's just there.

00:49:31.240 --> 00:49:38.102
And the sound is being carried upon the river like that.

00:49:38.102 --> 00:49:42.187
It's worship and the sound is carrying.

00:49:42.187 --> 00:49:50.160
I don't know how to describe it with words, but I could hear it.

00:49:50.160 --> 00:49:54.989
It sounded like 'Holy, holy, holy is the Lord.

00:49:54.989 --> 00:50:00.444
' That's what it sounded like.

00:50:00.444 --> 00:50:01.057
But beautiful.

00:50:04.817 --> 00:50:05.208
The very atmosphere is charged with worship.

00:50:05.208 --> 00:50:12.648
Wherever I'm at right now, when I was there five seconds ago, I could see it so clear.

00:50:12.648 --> 00:50:20.040
You know, we wonder why so many don't come back when we ask them to after being raised from the dead.

00:50:20.040 --> 00:50:36.880
Because once you taste that glory, there's nothing in this world that you would ever want to come back to.

00:50:36.880 --> 00:50:41.340
That instant what I just had for that split second was beautiful.

00:50:41.340 --> 00:50:45.345
Heaven is so real.

00:50:45.345 --> 00:50:51.760
It's just one breath away.

00:51:05.839 --> 00:51:06.148
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:51:06.148 --> 00:51:16.719
And then when you are a believing believer and you step over into that glory, no wonder nobody wants to come back.

00:51:16.719 --> 00:51:21.100
We say we can raise the dead, but they fight.

00:51:21.100 --> 00:51:25.226
They fight with everything, saying 'I don't want to come back to that.

00:51:25.226 --> 00:51:33.589
' You know that little boy—Heaven is for Real, you know.

00:51:33.599 --> 00:51:37.541
And he's like, 'Are you kidding me?

00:51:37.541 --> 00:51:54.133
' when you step over there and you just have that one little glimpse, like I just got to touch it for a second for whatever reason.

00:51:58.751 --> 00:52:02.480
The sound is carried and it's endless, but they're all one voice worshiping the Father and it's purples and beautiful pinks.

00:52:02.480 --> 00:52:04.691
It's so strange.

00:52:18.613 --> 00:52:18.871
You know what?

00:52:19.128 --> 00:52:20.160
I have these visitations.

00:52:25.133 --> 00:52:25.520
I usually am off camera and I can grasp it.

00:52:33.920 --> 00:52:35.264
But when there's 7,000 people watching you, it's kind of different when he comes and visits.

00:52:35.264 --> 00:52:36.811
Heaven is getting so close.

00:52:36.811 --> 00:52:41.040
Heaven is becoming so real.

00:52:41.040 --> 00:52:42.040
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:52:51.297 --> 00:52:51.502
And there's so many people that are asleep.

00:52:52.319 --> 00:52:57.789
I tried to warn you.

00:52:57.789 --> 00:53:08.380
He's standing at the door and there's so many people that are not ready for what's about to take place.

00:53:08.380 --> 00:53:11.839
There's so many people that are not ready for what's coming to America and these countries around the world.

00:53:16.000 --> 00:53:18.640
It's so important that you have a relationship with Jesus.

00:53:18.640 --> 00:53:24.160
Well, you say, 'Brother Brandon, I don't have a relationship like you do.

00:53:24.160 --> 00:53:31.932
' I've tried to tell you a thousand times I'm nothing special.

00:53:33.921 --> 00:53:36.400
I just decided to follow him.

00:53:41.180 --> 00:53:41.880
I chose to seek him just like you do anything.

00:53:41.880 --> 00:53:47.680
How bad do you want it in your life?

00:54:13.379 --> 00:54:13.609
It's not just going to happen.

00:54:13.609 --> 00:54:25.109
You're looking for a microwave, but everything in the spirit is not a microwave.

00:54:25.119 --> 00:54:27.744
Well, Brandon, you do two-hour prayer.

00:54:27.744 --> 00:54:29.147
This is nothing.

00:54:29.147 --> 00:54:31.015
This is my life.

00:54:42.667 --> 00:54:46.079
It costs a lot, but once you can push through that veil, he visits all the time and he has relationship with me.

00:54:46.079 --> 00:54:47.643
But it started out with nothing.

00:54:58.480 --> 00:54:58.667
I chose to fast.

00:55:00.960 --> 00:55:33.025
I chose to seek him and listen to tapes and follow him and clean and do what he asked me to do even when my flesh didn't want to do it.

00:55:33.025 --> 00:55:52.693
Stay at this house 20 years in a rat-shack house.

00:55:52.693 --> 00:56:05.832
Do what I ask you to do.

00:56:05.832 --> 00:56:32.320
Sit before the dryer and pray five hours a night, six hours a night.

00:56:32.320 --> 00:56:43.084
Sit there and leave your family.

00:57:15.574 --> 00:57:16.601
I want you to do this.

00:57:35.559 --> 00:57:35.809
You sit there and you listen.

00:57:35.809 --> 00:57:38.617
You sit in the cold.

00:57:45.293 --> 00:57:45.627
But I just sit and I make a place for him.

00:57:45.627 --> 00:57:48.811
How do you do that?

00:57:48.811 --> 00:57:51.748
I cultivate his presence.

00:57:51.748 --> 00:58:00.720
I keep a place for him in my heart and keep right before him by repenting.

00:58:19.680 --> 00:58:19.830
I am in a place of communion all around me.

00:58:23.710 --> 00:58:23.880
I have buckets of them.

00:58:37.413 --> 00:58:37.804
You say, 'Well, I only do that once in a while.

00:58:37.804 --> 00:58:42.720
' I take it all the time.

00:58:42.720 --> 00:58:45.936
I got them in my car.

00:58:45.936 --> 00:58:53.039
I got them in my living room.

00:58:53.039 --> 00:58:56.799
I've got them in my bathroom.

00:58:56.799 --> 00:58:58.888
I got communion everywhere.

00:58:58.888 --> 00:58:59.723
Why?

00:58:59.723 --> 00:59:08.740
Because in case I need it, I cultivate his presence.

00:59:08.740 --> 00:59:18.193
I teach my kids to do the same thing.

00:59:18.193 --> 00:59:26.895
My little girl, my boy, my wife, we just pursue him with all we have.

00:59:37.920 --> 00:59:38.190
But you have the same opportunity as me.

00:59:38.190 --> 00:59:42.045
Everybody has the opportunity to find books to read.

00:59:42.045 --> 00:59:50.188
It's like Diana said: 'Brendan, we should just spend today—don't go on live.

00:59:50.188 --> 01:00:10.960
Let's spend the day reading and doing things together,' because that's where we find Him.

01:00:10.960 --> 01:00:29.332
Reading Robert's book, 'The Ultimate Voice'—we want to go to the next level; we're not satisfied with here.

01:00:43.520 --> 01:00:44.120
This is wonderful, but I know there's more.

01:00:44.120 --> 01:00:45.920
There's more.

01:00:45.920 --> 01:01:03.480
If the angels can go around His throne and see something new every single time for eons and eons, 'Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts,' because they're seeing a new revelation, a new glimpse of the glory.

01:01:03.480 --> 01:01:07.405
And that came out of John Bevere's book.

01:01:07.405 --> 01:01:24.666
He's talking about it grabbing hold of people that want something deep and intimate with Him.

01:01:24.666 --> 01:01:35.640
Finding books that would inspire you, like 'The Awe of God.

01:01:35.640 --> 01:01:44.845
' Finding books that challenge your flesh to shut up because He's not going to yell.

01:01:44.845 --> 01:01:47.066
He's that still small voice.

01:02:26.610 --> 01:02:27.320
And you have so much clutter from the world outside of you that you can't hear Him.

01:02:27.320 --> 01:02:39.435
Turn up His volume and turn down yours.

01:03:23.200 --> 01:03:23.693
And the only way you're going to do that is by sitting at His feet.

01:04:03.110 --> 01:04:03.540
In the car, praying—I told Diana I was so tired of all the snow today.

01:04:57.711 --> 01:04:58.623
I said, 'Let's just drive in the snow.

01:04:58.623 --> 01:05:27.519
Put our SUV in gear and we'll drive around and we'll do the best we can.

01:05:27.519 --> 01:05:48.733
I've got to get out and pray over the city.

01:05:48.733 --> 01:06:02.713
' So I pray; it's a habit for me.

01:06:02.713 --> 01:06:34.555
It's probably as much as what somebody would say: 'I crave a salad.

01:06:34.555 --> 01:06:57.039
' Not me—my flesh, you can see—but I crave Him.

01:06:57.039 --> 01:07:18.448
He deals with all the other stuff.

01:07:18.448 --> 01:07:27.781
He corrects; He corrects those He loves.

01:07:34.640 --> 01:07:43.920
I would say if you're not being corrected, I would check my walk with Him.

01:07:43.920 --> 01:07:50.548
He corrects me more than I think He does a lot of people.

01:07:50.548 --> 01:08:08.079
I told Diana, 'I walk a very thin noodle with the Lord' with who I talk to and my conversations on the phone, everything.

01:08:08.079 --> 01:08:12.186
I get off and I get corrected.

01:08:12.186 --> 01:08:14.960
I walk a very fine line.

01:08:18.640 --> 01:08:22.171
The wider the road, the more He's not influencing.

01:08:22.171 --> 01:08:29.793
I feel the smaller the noodle—you're walking on a thin string.

01:08:29.793 --> 01:08:38.320
That means you're really walking with Him because He has an opinion about everything and He corrects about everything.

01:08:38.320 --> 01:08:44.209
This is what I want you to do: 'Come up higher.

01:09:00.790 --> 01:09:01.440
You must come up higher.

01:09:01.440 --> 01:09:06.560
' But I'm telling you, we're running out of time.

01:09:06.560 --> 01:09:12.080
The greatest outpouring of the Spirit is about to happen.

01:09:12.080 --> 01:09:17.247
Will you be a part of it?

01:09:17.247 --> 01:09:20.605
Will you help Him bring in the harvest?

01:09:22.648 --> 01:09:27.359
I know that the Son of the Lord, the man Jesus, is coming.

01:09:27.359 --> 01:09:28.400
He's coming.

01:09:55.269 --> 01:09:55.634
And there's so many people that even tonight, they're not ready.

